These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, turquise
1. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes turquise is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| Color     | turquise    | black   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, guinea-pig
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goldfish        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Flower   | dahlia    | amaryllis |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, mango
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | daisy |
| Food       | broccoli | mango    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, tiparillo
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, polish
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Cigar           | prince | tiparillo |
| Nationality   | polish    | dutch         |

 #################################

 
