2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana
1. the vegafina-smoker is the fan of disco##1
2. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | disco   |
| Cigar   | havana | vegafina |

